{
  "stem": "23498.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The second row, someone get-- got, you know, one step forward, and they pushed me to get one step forward.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was seen, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Prague. ?] They were building something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- they were erecting a big building, the Germans, and the Jews were working as workers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But by the same time, they were-- they were bringing some valuable things for exchange for food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we, the women-- a few women who were working also, they were in the kitchen, like with a caretaker-- it was a caretaker.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were-- and for the first time, I had a good meal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave me something to eat, and all of a sudden, the German comes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the caretakers said, Germans are coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I lied down on-- under the bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I-- I had long legs, you know, and he noticed me, and others.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I help in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, of course, he didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- you're going to Umschlagplatz, he said straightaway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he went to catch us, because it wasn't his duty to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And keep them here, and he went to get other Germans-- to-- to call other Germans to take us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was some force, which I can't understand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just-- after him, I just ran, and I kept running.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a Polish girl was leaving in the next door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I met her there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to the last floor, and I was waiting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was on the [INAUDIBLE] side already, with the [INAUDIBLE], which is people who are working on the [INAUDIBLE] side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was caught among others by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was autumn '42.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
